songs.title: Pain*
songs.lyrics:
[Chorus]
Anxiety, Meth with some, um, yeah
Pills & Anxiety, they take control, (Oh)
Anxiety, Meth with some, um, ah
Pills & Anxiety, they take control, Yeah

[Post-Chorus]
Bad Timing, Stars aligning
Lost in my abyss, please someone find me
Bad Timing, Stars aligning
They don't wanna see me win
Crucify the kid

[Verse]
Feeling terrible, oh, this unbearable pain
Lost in my head, yeah, losing my brain
Anybody else tryna get to me, they abusing my brain
Even when I'm doing drugs, shit don't feel the same
Beautiful, uh, incredible pain
No matter how hard I try, can't get other people to change
Beautiful, see it through my cubical, (Aye)
She still got a lot to learn, so do I so it's okay
You're not right all the time, neither am I
I need you by my side, now I feel dry
You're the only one that can convince me that I won't die
You're not the one in my movie, happily, I'm that nigga Nicolas Cage

[Chorus]
Anxiety, Meth with some, um, yeah
Pills & Anxiety, they take control, (Oh)
Anxiety, Meth with some, um, ah
Pills & Anxiety, they take control, Yeah

[Post-Chorus]
Bad Timing, Stars aligning
Lost in my abyss, please someone find me
Bad Timing, Stars aligning
They don't wanna see me win
Crucify the kid
